<section class="static-content blue-wrap blue-wrap-padding">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="content-body">
      <p style="font-weight: 400;">The NCBA logbook loan product aims to give individuals and businesses access to quick financing to enable them to meet their emergency needs for immediate cash.</p>
<p style="font-weight: 400;">You are able to borrow cash against an owned vehicle, provided its not under any finance.</p>
<p style="font-weight: 400;">Features:</p>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;">Minimum loan amount- RWF 1 Million</li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;">NCBA Bank Rwanda will finance up to 30% of cars under 12 years for a repayment period of 3 years.</li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;">Logbook loan applicable to Private and commercial vehicles only, i.e. Trucks, Saloon cars and pickups. PSV vehicles such as buses, Matatus, Taxis, etc.  Not applicable</li>
</ul>
<p style="font-weight: 400;">Benefits:</p>
<ul>
<li>Access to quick financing against the car value.</li>
<li>Repayment cycle based on customers income cycle.</li>
<li>Loan application feedback in 48 hours.</li>
</ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
